    </ul></nav><!-- .menu_breadcrumb //--><h1 class="fbcms_content fbcms_replacementcontent fbcms_plaintext inside_title" id="content_33569">COVID-19 Closure Info</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="center_content">
                    <div class="fbcms_content fbcms_richtext inside_center" id="content_33570">
    <div class="fbcms_richtext_content">
        <h2>Information &amp; Resources<img alt="" class="Right_Align_With_Padding" src="/downloads/district/covid19-badge250.png" style="height:135px; width:250px">
</h2>

<ul>
<li>
	<p>Please read <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/11zmWFRdcyvaRq_e-B8TK70HUkXcBBX2z2PCDyiGTpJQ/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank">this important letter</a> from Assistant Superintendent Meaghan Gauthier.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>Under Governor's Executive 2020-21, Alpena Public Schools have closed the Administration Building. Employees in various departments are working remotely from home. If you need to talk to someone in a particular department, please call the following numbers:</p>

	<ul>
<li>Business Office - 358-5000</li>
		<li>Enrollment Office - 358-5025</li>
		<li>Human Resources - 358-5032</li>
		<li>Food Service - 358-5020</li>
		<li>Superintendent's Office - 358-5042</li>
	</ul>
</li>
	<li>The district has formulated an approved Continuity of Learning Plan. The plan and the approval document are posted for review <a href="/district/administration/continuity-of-learning-plan/" title="Continuity of Learning Plan">here</a>.</li>
	<li>
<a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1q1KkyiLawZF84vkBSweO88_b5PC4B2Rr6RDUFo2YKEE/edit" target="_blank">APS Food Distribution</a> - Note this document is updated as needed, so check back often.</li>
	<li><strong>Access to Internet - Charter will offer free Spectrum broadband and Wi-Fi access for 60 days to households with K-12 and/or college students who do not already have a Spectrum broadband subscription at any service level up to 100 Mbps. To enroll call 1-844-488-8395. Installation fees will be waived for new student households. (Note that this offer is direct from the company and is not affiliated with or supported by APS.)</strong></li>
	<li>
<a href="https://www.mi211.org/" target="_blank">211</a> - Dial 211 to get help with food, housing, paying bills, family crisis, etc.</li>
	<li>
<a href="https://www.nemcsa.org/news-events/resources-available-in-your-community?fbclid=IwAR3hEE5SOQ1pRHBxF4Mbc_MCM2W_6d8noSEq1ExNiHhvgImFYkqZbsL21Ro" target="_blank">NEMSCA Resources</a> - Get information on local resources and how they have been modified due to COVID-19.</li>
	<li>
<a href="https://www.dhd4.org/" target="_blank">District Health Department #4</a> - Track how many tests have been given in this service area.</li>
	<li>If your family has experienced a change in income, you may be newly eligible for food assistance benefits. See this information about the <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1sF0d14bL7M5loGWqQ3AwhYRAHdN_G0X__KiRH7K7wws/edit#heading=h.xu8hxk7erah7" target="_blank">Pandemic EBT Program</a>.</li>
</ul>
<h2>FAQs</h2>

<p>Click to view the latest version of our <a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1jAfZv9_xTrOmgGERu3Svrj5QmzuuR_BZJKzpQkiieHA/edit" target="_blank">Frequently Asked Questions</a>. Check back often and we will updated the information to reflect any changes.</p>

<h2>Educational Resources</h2>

<p>Visit our <a href="/student-resources/">For Students</a> page for lots of resources and ideas to keep students' minds engaged and learning during the closure. <strong>Note that all activities are optional.</strong> APS is not requiring or assigning any work at this time.</p>

<h2>Chromebook Loans Available</h2>

<p>If your student does not have access to appropriate technology (such as a laptop or desktop computer), APS will loan a Chromebook to your family for use during the emergency closure. Complete the online <a href="https://forms.gle/Spm73QZHyyQmW8sU7" target="_blank">Chromebook  Checkout Form</a> or call 989-358-5029. Chromebooks can be picked up at AHS on food distribution days (<a href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1q1KkyiLawZF84vkBSweO88_b5PC4B2Rr6RDUFo2YKEE/edit" target="_blank">schedule</a>). Please allow 24 hours lead time.</p>

<p>Chromebooks required internet access. If you do not have internet access at home, see the offer from Charter/Spectrum above.</p>
